        <hl1>An Open Border With Mexico?</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Prof Jorge A Bustamante replies to Aug 24 editorial voicing skepticism about Pres-elect Vincente Fox's ideas for free labor movement across Mexican border</p>
      </abstract>
